{"tid":876471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【超強颱風玉兔】天文台提早發預測路徑 料勁過山竹 膺今年風王","createTime":"2018-10-25T15:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T16:23:42.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"464a6c811283eddfcb53ee44c3ca61e0359c6523","tid":876471,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"【超強颱風玉兔】天文台提早發預測路徑 料勁過山竹 膺今年風王<br />\n<br />\n【新增澳門當局預測】<br />\n<br />\n上月帶來35年最強10號波的強颱風「山竹」，吹襲菲律賓呂qq5宋島前，香港天文台當時評定其中心風力加強至時速250公里，是今年西北太平洋最強颱風，惟其「寶座」將很快被取代。昨晚吹襲美國關島的超強颱風「玉兔」，未來一兩日將進一步增強，香港天文台預計其中心風力或加強至時速260公里，超越山竹，成為今年的新「風王」。<br />\n<br />\n一般而言，當風暴西移至東經140&deg;內，香港天文台才公佈官方和電腦預測路徑。但因應公眾和傳媒相當關注「玉兔」的動向，天文台未待玉兔進入東經140&deg;，昨已在facebook，率先貼出由電腦運算的風暴路徑概率預測圖，解釋玉兔未來路徑有何變數，今早亦提早發佈官方的預測路徑，預計玉兔未來5日一直西移，靠近呂宋以東海域，重申玉兔下周初的路徑仍有變數。<br />\n<br />\n澳門氣象局傍晚發特別報告，指玉兔未來數天大致趨向台灣至菲律賓以東海域，綜合現時預報資料，認為玉兔下周一（29日）前，進入南海機會不大，未有進一步評估其後走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181025/large/1540444123_3319.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F1540444123_3319.png&h=82b31534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181025/58833858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58833858&d=eMvUS6xmk1IgPRkUV4eKmHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=21753725\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58833858&h=64b776c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181025/58833858</a>"},{"pid":"a50e6aa9d97c2510375d58ed741837d89a0c42e7","tid":876471,"uid":45148,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 預測：<br />\n過左菲律賓就無哂風力<br />\n季後風會大幅減弱佢"},{"pid":"f3a180f089c5c75f448a7321e68c0b2d0ad0e475","tid":876471,"uid":58880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"港珠澳同高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74750744253fe98e95341b13d91d5d8e45a8664b","tid":876471,"uid":91321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"又吹大佢，入到南海重有命先算啦<br />\n11月都嚟緊"},{"pid":"b0405d17d5cef6c860201a7381f86117f88c8aed","tid":876471,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"依個時候入南海 應該連 颱風級數都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3608efeffce84ead9690bba24a161fda56ec6f5c","tid":876471,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"一過菲律賓就減弱，把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd44f71feeab6a33cf454f4cbcccb3e8d9a8968b","tid":876471,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"玉兔生不逢時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c91355883c02c7b9b6345d51cfe129ebfdb83e","tid":876471,"uid":63287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"天交合正on"},{"pid":"496b4c5143c880a8097072a51cc1a01a1f669f19","tid":876471,"uid":58484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0547736e85a6cc926f35e6757cde9d011bd994cf","tid":876471,"uid":95497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"未被壓走咗先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1abd317c5717e39f33a1a0fb50c457f13f26c1","tid":876471,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YCUoB0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i